data.description: Beautiful home on a corner lot with an open floor plan that has modern light fixtures, insulated windows, and Ash Wood tile flooring. Large kitchen with a pantry and the island has cabinets and also includes built in bookshelves on the sides. Master suite has 2 closets plus a private bath with walk in shower, garden tub, double vanities, and a linen closet. One of the secondary bedrooms has two large closets and a bathroom shared with main living area. The other 2 secondary bedrooms have a shared bathroom connected to each room. All bedrooms have ceiling fans. All doorways except for the shared bathroom are wheelchair accessible. Master shower will accommodate a wheelchair and shower chair, and has a professionally installed grab bar and an adjustable height handheld shower nozzle. Laundry room has an extra countertop with cabinets. There is a large covered patio with double ceiling fans. Security system to stay with home.
